                            </cit>: si quis duas uxores duxerit <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወኢሰደደ፡ ዳግሚተ፡ ዘይእቲ፡ ሕርትምት፡</foreign> F.M. 5,4; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰብሳብ፡ ርኵስት፡ ወሕርትምት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="F.M." loc=" 9,4">F.M.  9,4</ref> (sed in titulo capitis <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕርምት፡</foreign> scriptum est); <foreign xml:lang="gez">ረባሕ፡ ርኵስት፡ ወሕርትምት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="F.M." loc=" 18,1.">F.M.  18,1.</ref> (In <ref cRef="Sx. Tachs." loc="13">Sx. Tachs. 13</ref> legitur <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕርትምት፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                                <quote> votum </quote>
                            </cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትሕርምት፡</foreign>).</sense> </sense>
               
